
@access_token = <SET_TOKEN_HERE> //hier token einfügen

### 1) Projekt anlegen → erwartet 201 Created + JSON + Location
POST http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "designation": "LF08 PMS",
  "responsibleEmployeeId": 1,
  "customerId": 2,
  "customerContactPerson": "Max",
  "comment": "Demo",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01"
}

> {%
    const b = typeof response.body === 'string' ? JSON.parse(response.body) : response.body;
    if (b && b.id) client.global.set("project_id", String(b.id));
%}

###

### 2) (optional) Projekt per ID abrufen
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/{{project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

